No, just have - the same. She baked - you see, the difference in those days were that she baked twice a week. She baked - she baked tea cakes you see, she'd bake the cakes and she'd bake what we called a fatty
 cake, that's a big - a big round - aye, aye, yes, yes, and we'd all such as that you know. Something that was substantial you see. See she - we were brought up together you know, practically.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 So you mainly had bread with a bit of bacon at breakfast time?
