\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 At dinner time, your father didn't come home for his dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 No, no.
