\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 Yes. Oh yes. Used to get fed right you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 When you got home at tea time would your father be there as well?
