\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 No, it - we left school at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 15}}
