\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 Yes. Yes. Oh yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 Sort of an afternoon sort of tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 Yes. Yes.
