\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 You don't remember her making any wine at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14512253 PS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables or fruit?
