ng. But when the war broke out - there were a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7561684\charrsid13133166 piece}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 
 up in the quarry that he dug up. And I didn't - I - I hardly knew that when I came back - well I came home on leave from France twice you see during the war and - they were dig - they were - they had dug 
up for themselves for the war then - never before that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 What did he grow up there, do you know?
