Well he'd grow - he'd grow potatoes and cabbage and such as that you know. All to - oh - come in for the house you see, 'cos - because it were wartime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6240188 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16188304\charrsid13133166 But not before the war?
